2\n          },\n          \"senderLabel\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Lead is asking again for the same thing - MCP Stitch folder not appearing after setup. I've already done this work and pushed to branch `feat/full-setup-mcp`. Lead might not have seen the previous response, or they're on the old branch.\\n\\nLet me just give a very concise reply with the exact command to switch to the new branch and test.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"\\nDạ Lead, đã xong rồi ạ! Đang ở branch `feat/full-setup-mcp`. \\n\\nLead chạy lệnh này trên máy cần setup:\\n\\n```bash\\n# Xóa bản cũ\\nrm -rf ~/.openclaw-setup\\n\\n# Clone branch mới\\ngit clone -b feat/full-setup-mcp https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git ~/.openclaw-setup\\n\\n# Chạy setup\\ncd ~/.openclaw-setup && ./install.sh dev\\n```\\n\\nSau setup xong sẽ có đủ:\\n```\\n~/.openclaw/mcp-servers/gitlab/      ✅\\n~/.openclaw/mcp-servers/confluence/  ✅  \\n~/.openclaw/mcp-servers/stitch/      ✅ (MỚI)\\n~/.openclaw/workspaces/              ✅ 13 agents\\n~/.openclaw/skills/                  ✅ skills\\n~/.openclaw/openclaw.json           ✅ config\\n```\\n\\nSau đó:\\n```bash\\nopenclaw gateway restart\\nopenclaw status\\n```\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 301,\n            \"totalTokens\": 72422,\n            \"cacheRead\": 72121,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776258286333,\n          \"responseId\": \"062ebfef84b6e1f19cad0f72923001c8\",\n          \"