{"type":"message","id":"a9667366","parentId":"7783efa8","timestamp":"2026-04-15T13:45:43.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the current state vs. the last known state.\n\n**Last known state (from heartbeat-state.json):**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` - running\n- `cron:6f3323ef` - running\n- `master-orchestrator:main` - running\n- `subagent:52f0c795` - done\n- `subagent:63bb70ce` - done\n- `subagent:ba49ac6d` - done\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` - done\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` - done\n- 6 pre-existing failures\n\n\n- 2 active sessions\n\n**Current state (from sessions_list):**\nThe orchestrator cron is still running as expected, and the DTLX 5p progress cron has now failed, whereas it was running before. The master-orchestrator main session is now done instead of running, and the telegram sender subagent is still done.\n\nLooking at the broader picture, most of the older sessions have already completed or failed as expected, but I notice `cron:6f3323ef` has transitioned from running to failed, and there's another orchestrator cron running that appears to be the DTLX version based on the timestamp.\n\nThe main orchestrator session has shifted from running to done, and I can see the 5p progress report cron spawned child sessions to handle the reporting work.\n\nLet me compare the last known state against what I'm seeing now to identify what actually changed between then and now.\n\nThe cron job for DTLX 15p progress appears to have crashed—it went from running to failed with a 502 error, and there's no new cron running in its place. Meanwhile, the main orchestrator session has completed its work. The child sessions from the new cron are still active, but the cron itself has failed, and the old pre-existing failures remain as they were.\n\nLooking at what's changed since the last report, the DTLX cron has failed while the QLHV cron is still running normally. I need to notify the group about this status change, and I should also save this updated state to the heartbeat file for future comparisons.","thinkingSignature":"8756d11154c7264bfb38577d3a1a632d1ef531a9a5db959c234713010ec77810"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me update the state file and send the report:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s2dscenyla58_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json","content":"{\n  \"savedAt\": \"2026-04-15T13:44:00Z\",\n  \"sessions\": {\n    \"cron:ed2d0b5d\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"note\": \"QLHV 15p cron - running at 13:44 UTC\" },\n    \"cron:6f3323ef\": { \"status\": \"failed\", \"note\": \"DTLX 15p cron - FAILED at 13:40 UTC (502 upstream unavailable)\" },\n    \"master-orchestrator:main\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"note\": \"interactive session completed at ~13:33 UTC\" },\n    \"telegram:direct:6053576134\": { \"status\": \"done\" },\n    \"telegram:group:-5163901258\": { \"status\": \"done\" },\n    \"preExistingFailures\": [\n      \"senior-backend:subagent:2e5ea409 (failed, 2026-04-12, old)\",\n      \"senior-backend:subagent:e3ca11a2 (killed, 2026-04-12, old)\",\n      \"ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:ae038bd3 (failed, 2026-04-12, old)\",\n      \"ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:469f1534 (failed, 2026-04-12, old)\",\n      \"senior-frontend:subagent:cf1f74df (failed, 2026-04-12, old)\",\n      \"senior-backend:subagent:f42cdd0e (failed, 2026-04-12, old)\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"activeCount\": 1,\n  \"preExistingFailures\": 6,\n  \"blockers\": 1,\n  \"changes\": [\n    \"FAILED: cron:6f3323ef (DTLX 15p progress) — 502 Upstream unavailable, delivery stopped\",\n    \"COMPLETED: master-orchestrator:main — interactive session finished normally\"\n  ]\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":23076,"output":962,"cacheRead":14726,"cacheWrite":432,"totalTokens":39196,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopRe